      <title>分析师称，欧​​盟乌克兰融资计划可能进一步提振央行黄金购买</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/eus-ukraine-funding-plan-could-further-boost-central-bank-gold-buying-analysts-2025-10-14/</link>
